title: We're getting a new champion again?

Definitely Not...

At first, I thought it was Vel'Koz. Then I thought to myself "Self, that is definitely NOT Vel'Koz."

I bet it's some weird champion that's just utterly busted.

I bet it's name is Yorick.

I bet it'll get nerfed a lot.

I bet it'll never see any skins for years.

I bet Riot will hate it because it does tonnes of damage.

I bet it'll be the least played champion in the game after he's nerfed so much.

I bet it's name is Yorick.

http://www.auplod.com/u/loaupd78608.png
He looks pretty boring to me, why would I want to play some normal, average-looking guy on his way to work over all the monsters, mages, and knights this game has to offer?
